{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"show","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"YES to show alerts in foreground, NO to suppress them (default)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"show"}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, iOS does not display notification banners when the app is in the foreground.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Enable this to show system notification alerts even when the app is active.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Configure based on app type:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class NotificationConfigManager {","","    func configureForAppType(_ appType: AppType) {","        switch appType {","        case .messaging:","            \/\/ Messaging apps typically handle notifications in-app","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        case .ecommerce, .news:","            \/\/ E-commerce and news apps benefit from showing all notifications","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(true)","","        case .game:","            \/\/ Games might want to suppress during gameplay","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","        }","    }","","    func temporarilyDisableForegroundAlerts(during action: () -> Void) {","        let wasEnabled = Pushwoosh.configure.getShowPushnotificationAlert()","        Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        action()","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(wasEnabled)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate"},{"text":" and use ","type":"text"},{"code":"Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setShowPushnotificationAlert:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setShowPushnotificationAlert:","symbolKind":"method"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets whether to show alert for push notifications when app is in foreground."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setshowpushnotificationalert:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","title":"PushwooshCore","role":"collection","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PW